{"title":"Kubernetes Events Dashboard Header","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"# Kubernetes Events

This dashboard displays Kubernetes events generated during the specified time period.  You can filter the events to a specific namespace or pod by clicking on the appropriate filter displayed above and editing the filter.  After updating the filter and hitting __[SAVE]__, remember to _enable_ the updated filter (via the RMB pop-up menu) to have it take effect.

The ***kube.namespace***, ***properties.object*** and ***properties.object_type*** columns identify the namespace,  object name and the type of object (generally a pod) which generated the event."},"aggs":[]}
